Package pkgMain

Class Histogram

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Histogram
public class Histogram
extends java.lang.Object
This file organizes the data for the leps in the garden and creates a histogram with this data. References: http://java-buddy.blogspot.com/2015/07/javafx-barchart-example-plot-data.html
Author:
Allie
